I think there's been a misunderstanding! I'm not the one reading the book, you are! I'm just an AI, I don't have personal experiences or read books. I'm here to help you and provide information.

But I'd love to hear more about your experience with the book! Is there a particular chapter or section that's resonating with you? Have you learned any new strategies or insights that are helping you with sleep or relaxation?
